<h4>nsukLib is simple and easy to use</h4>
<p></p>
<h4> Adding Books</h4>
<p> Adding books in nsukLib App is easy: </p>
<ul>
    <li>
        Tap on the menu or Swipe on the navigation drawer and click <b>Settings
    </b> then <b>Add a book </b>, fill in the book detail
        and <b>Upload</b> it to the database.
    </li>
</ul>

<ul>
    <li>
        You can equally delete a book from the database by
        providing an <b>ISBN </b> of the book you want deleted.
    </li>
</ul>

<h4>Barcode</h4>
<p> Barcode Scanner: </p>
<ul>
    <li>
        nsukLib App provide an easy way to scan any barcode file by clicking on the
        <b>barcode</b> on the menu list item.
    </li>
</ul>
<h4>Share</h4>
<p>Sharing File: </p>
<ul>
    <li>
        You can easily <b>Share</b> your files saved on the phone through an
        Email App or any other app installed on the phone.
    </li>
    <li>
        After making requested booking in order to confirm your reservation,
        you can use the <b>Share</b> button to send the generated <b>QR Image</b>
        to the school library admin email address for your confirmation.
    </li>
</ul>
<h4>Search</h4>
<p>Searching books: </p>
<ul>
    <li>
        The <b>Search</b> button enables you to filter through the list of books by <b>Author</b>
    </li>
    <li>
        You can click on the desired book to get the full details that includes <b>ISBN</b> and
        <b>publication date</b>.
    </li>
    <li>
        Select a <b>pick up date </b> if you want to make a reservation.
        Follow the prompt and save your generated barcode.</p>
    </li>
</ul>

<h4>Questions, Comments and Bug Reporting</h4>
<ul>
    <li>
        Click on the top drawer and the <b>About</b> page for our contact details.
    </li>
</ul>

</body>
</html>
